cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper is about the development and evaluation of algorithms for automatic detection of pulmonary nodules in thoracic CT scans. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) as it involves the use of image analysis and pattern recognition techniques to identify nodules. Information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible categories as the paper deals with the analysis of medical images.
